conversations.subject: SUBJECT: Re: Santanderca Banking is a micro
conversations.body:
Hello Gail,
I acknowledge the receipt of your mail.(How long does it take to receive 
my funds after I have applied?) But first I have to tell you it will 
take less than two weeks to receive the funds, I must confirm wisely.
Note that the Investor would be willing to invest in any area of the 
project depending on how attractive the business plan is and would 
return good interest (annually) as he might not be interested in minor 
tasks.
Funds will be released per your demand if you meet his requirements by 
indicating proper and attractive investment intent to see if he will be 
interested in the investment and earn good profit within ten years. 
After that, the fund is without interest but willing to share gain from 
the invested sum or an inevitable return on investment.
In your return mail, please provide your business plan and show your 
capability to manage huge funds and state the amount. Your company must 
deliver excellent and sustainable returns on investment to the Investor 
annually.
If the Investor accepts your business plan, I assure you that funding 
will be approved immediately.
Please confirm by return mail your private telephone number.
Furthermore, we will schedule a virtual (zoom or skype) meeting between 
us /the representative, and you on the project.
The meeting matter will be on the following subject matter.
Step 1: Project Objectives.
Step 2: The interest rate, security component, and terms. (The Investor 
might require between 3.5% to 9% depending on the required amount).
Step 3: Check the Eligibility Criteria.
Once I receive your response, we will provide a non-disclosure agreement 
and KYC, which you will fill out and sign to enable us to start the 
introduction process with the Investor. It will also be essential that 
you provide a detailed business plan.
We will also issue you the direct contact of the investor/Mandate for a 
virtual call via skype or zoom meeting once the time is due.
Sincerely,
2171 Douglas Ave,
  North Battleford SK S9A3N9
  Canada.
